{
  "video_id": "0R9zjn9BBvA",
  "title": "You are fluent in this language (and don't even know it) | Christoph Niemann",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 14000.0,
      "text": "I'm an artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15240.0,
      "end_time": 17880.0,
      "text": "Being an artist is the greatest job there is."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18760.0,
      "end_time": 21560.0,
      "text": "And I really pity each and every one of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21800.0,
      "end_time": 23776.0,
      "text": "who has to spend your days discovering new galaxies"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23800.0,
      "end_time": 26456.0,
      "text": "or saving humanity from global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26480.0,
      "end_time": 28936.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28960.0,
      "end_time": 31880.0,
      "text": "But being an artist is also a daunting job."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32880.0,
      "end_time": 36480.0,
      "text": "I spend every day, from nine to six, doing this."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37200.0,
      "end_time": 39960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39120.0,
      "end_time": 43960.0,
      "text": "I even started a side career that consists entirely"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43120.0,
      "end_time": 45936.0,
      "text": "of complaining about the difficulty of the creative process."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45960.0,
      "end_time": 47560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47800.0,
      "end_time": 50839.0,
      "text": "But today, I don't want to talk about what makes my life difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51480.0,
      "end_time": 54960.0,
      "text": "I want to talk about what makes it easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54120.0,
      "end_time": 55616.0,
      "text": "And that is you"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55640.0,
      "end_time": 58296.0,
      "text": "and the fact that you are fluent in a language"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58320.0,
      "end_time": 60178.0,
      "text": "that you're probably not even aware of."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61480.0,
      "end_time": 64560.0,
      "text": "You're fluent in the language of reading images."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66720.0,
      "end_time": 68176.0,
      "text": "Deciphering an image like that"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68200.0,
      "end_time": 70256.0,
      "text": "takes quite a bit of an intellectual effort."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70280.0,
      "end_time": 72496.0,
      "text": "But nobody ever taught you how this works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72520.0,
      "end_time": 73759.0,
      "text": "you just know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75280.0,
      "end_time": 77376.0,
      "text": "College, shopping, music."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77400.0,
      "end_time": 81176.0,
      "text": "What makes a language powerful is that you can take a very complex idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81200.0,
      "end_time": 84800.0,
      "text": "and communicate it in a very simple, efficient form."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85760.0,
      "end_time": 88960.0,
      "text": "These images represent exactly the same ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90680.0,
      "end_time": 93960.0,
      "text": "But when you look, for example, at the college hat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93120.0,
      "end_time": 96536.0,
      "text": "you know that this doesn't represent the accessory you wear on your head"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96560.0,
      "end_time": 98416.0,
      "text": "when you're being handed your diploma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98440.0,
      "end_time": 100240.0,
      "text": "but rather the whole idea of college."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102400.0,
      "end_time": 106176.0,
      "text": "Now, what drawings can do is they cannot only communicate images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106200.0,
      "end_time": 109160.0,
      "text": "they can even evoke emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109400.0,
      "end_time": 112336.0,
      "text": "Let's say you get to an unfamiliar place and you see this."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112360.0,
      "end_time": 113936.0,
      "text": "You feel happiness and relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113960.0,
      "end_time": 115735.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115760.0,
      "end_time": 121176.0,
      "text": "Or a slight sense of unease or maybe downright panic."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121200.0,
      "end_time": 123736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123760.0,
      "end_time": 127216.0,
      "text": "Or blissful peace and quiet."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127240.0,
      "end_time": 128856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128880.0,
      "end_time": 132320.0,
      "text": "But visuals, they're of course more than just graphic icons."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133360.0,
      "end_time": 136736.0,
      "text": "You know, if I want to tell the story of modern-day struggle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136760.0,
      "end_time": 139976.0,
      "text": "I would start with the armrest between two airplane seats"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140000.0,
      "end_time": 142136.0,
      "text": "and two sets of elbows fighting."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142160.0,
      "end_time": 145550.0,
      "text": "What I love there is this universal law"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 145800.0,
      "end_time": 147496.0,
      "text": "that, you know, you have 30 seconds to fight it out"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147520.0,
      "end_time": 150696.0,
      "text": "and once it's yours, you get to keep it for the rest of the flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150720.0,
      "end_time": 152816.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152840.0,
      "end_time": 156736.0,
      "text": "Now, commercial flight is full of these images."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156760.0,
      "end_time": 160256.0,
      "text": "If I want to illustrate the idea of discomfort,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160280.0,
      "end_time": 162176.0,
      "text": "nothing better than these neck pillows."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162200.0,
      "end_time": 165256.0,
      "text": "They're designed to make you more comfortable --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 165280.0,
      "end_time": 167960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167120.0,
      "end_time": 168336.0,
      "text": "except they don't."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168360.0,
      "end_time": 171320.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172200.0,
      "end_time": 173640.0,
      "text": "So I never sleep on airplanes."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174880.0,
      "end_time": 178976.0,
      "text": "What I do occasionally is I fall into a sort of painful coma."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179000.0,
      "end_time": 182496.0,
      "text": "And when I wake up from that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182520.0,
      "end_time": 185176.0,
      "text": "I have the most terrible taste in my mouth."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185200.0,
      "end_time": 188536.0,
      "text": "It's a taste that's so bad, it cannot be described with words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 188560.0,
      "end_time": 189936.0,
      "text": "but it can be drawn."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189960.0,
      "end_time": 195896.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195920.0,
      "end_time": 198519.0,
      "text": "The thing is, you know, I love sleeping."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199160.0,
      "end_time": 202896.0,
      "text": "And when I sleep, I really prefer to do it while spooning."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 202920.0,
      "end_time": 206856.0,
      "text": "I've been spooning on almost a pro level for close to 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 206880.0,
      "end_time": 209775.0,
      "text": "but in all this time, I've never figured out"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209800.0,
      "end_time": 211456.0,
      "text": "what to do with that bottom arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211480.0,
      "end_time": 214960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 214120.0,
      "end_time": 216560.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216800.0,
      "end_time": 218360.0,
      "text": "And the only thing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219640.0,
      "end_time": 222495.0,
      "text": "the only thing that makes sleeping even more complicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 222520.0,
      "end_time": 224216.0,
      "text": "than trying to do it on an airplane"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 224240.0,
      "end_time": 225800.0,
      "text": "is when you have small children."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 227400.0,
      "end_time": 229790.0,
      "text": "They show up at your bed at around 4am"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 230400.0,
      "end_time": 233256.0,
      "text": "with some bogus excuse of, \"I had a bad dream.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 233280.0,
      "end_time": 235536.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 235560.0,
      "end_time": 238506.0,
      "text": "And then, of course you feel sorry for them, they're your kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 238520.0,
      "end_time": 239946.0,
      "text": "so you let them into your bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 239960.0,
      "end_time": 243675.0,
      "text": "And I have to admit, at the beginning, they're really cute and warm and snugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 243685.0,
      "end_time": 246856.0,
      "text": "The minute you fall back asleep, they inexplicably --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 246880.0,
      "end_time": 248536.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 248560.0,
      "end_time": 249816.0,
      "text": "start rotating."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 249840.0,
      "end_time": 252416.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 252440.0,
      "end_time": 254393.0,
      "text": "We like to call this the helicopter mode."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 254417.0,
      "end_time": 256256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 256279.0,
      "end_time": 261296.0,
      "text": "Now, the deeper something is etched into your consciousness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 261320.0,
      "end_time": 264680.0,
      "text": "the fewer details we need to have an emotional reaction."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 265360.0,
      "end_time": 268216.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 268240.0,
      "end_time": 270160.0,
      "text": "So why does an image like this work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 271000.0,
      "end_time": 273616.0,
      "text": "It works, because we as readers"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 273640.0,
      "end_time": 275880.0,
      "text": "are incredibly good at filling in the blanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277000.0,
      "end_time": 281160.0,
      "text": "Now, when you draw, there's this concept of negative space."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 281400.0,
      "end_time": 283936.0,
      "text": "And the idea is, that instead of drawing the actual object,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 283960.0,
      "end_time": 285976.0,
      "text": "you draw the space around it."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 286000.0,
      "end_time": 288400.0,
      "text": "So the bowls in this drawing are empty."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 289360.0,
      "end_time": 293240.0,
      "text": "But the black ink prompts your brain to project food into a void."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 296200.0,
      "end_time": 299360.0,
      "text": "What we see here is not a owl flying."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 300113.0,
      "end_time": 302256.0,
      "text": "What we actually see is a pair of AA batteries"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 302280.0,
      "end_time": 304455.0,
      "text": "standing on a nonsensical drawing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 304480.0,
      "end_time": 308160.0,
      "text": "and I animate the scene by moving my desk lamp up and down."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 308400.0,
      "end_time": 310960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 310120.0,
      "end_time": 312720.0,
      "text": "The image really only exists in your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 313640.0,
      "end_time": 316760.0,
      "text": "So, how much information do we need to trigger such an image?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 318400.0,
      "end_time": 322120.0,
      "text": "My goal as an artist is to use the smallest amount possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 323120.0,
      "end_time": 325936.0,
      "text": "I try to achieve a level of simplicity"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 325960.0,
      "end_time": 328376.0,
      "text": "where, if you were to take away one more element,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 328400.0,
      "end_time": 330440.0,
      "text": "the whole concept would just collapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 331520.0,
      "end_time": 335159.0,
      "text": "And that's why my personal favorite tool as an artist is abstraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 336520.0,
      "end_time": 339536.0,
      "text": "I've come up with this system which I call the abstract-o-meter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 339560.0,
      "end_time": 340896.0,
      "text": "and this is how it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 340920.0,
      "end_time": 344816.0,
      "text": "So you take a symbol, any symbol, for example the heart and the arrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 344840.0,
      "end_time": 347655.0,
      "text": "which most of us would read as the symbol for love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 347680.0,
      "end_time": 349496.0,
      "text": "and I'm an artist, so I can draw this"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 349520.0,
      "end_time": 352479.0,
      "text": "in any given degree of realism or abstraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 353320.0,
      "end_time": 357695.0,
      "text": "Now, if I go too realistic on it, it just grosses everybody out."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 357720.0,
      "end_time": 359736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 359760.0,
      "end_time": 363695.0,
      "text": "If I go too far on the other side and do very abstract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 363720.0,
      "end_time": 365976.0,
      "text": "nobody has any idea what they're looking at."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 366000.0,
      "end_time": 368376.0,
      "text": "So I have to find the perfect place on that scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 368400.0,
      "end_time": 370440.0,
      "text": "in this case it's somewhere in the middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 371320.0,
      "end_time": 374840.0,
      "text": "Now, once we have reduced an image to a more simple form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 376800.0,
      "end_time": 378200.0,
      "text": "all sorts of new connections become possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 380760.0,
      "end_time": 384536.0,
      "text": "And that allows for totally new angles in storytelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 384560.0,
      "end_time": 387936.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 387960.0,
      "end_time": 389416.0,
      "text": "And so, what I like to do is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 389440.0,
      "end_time": 393640.0,
      "text": "I like to take images from really remote cultural areas and bring them together."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396000.0,
      "end_time": 398376.0,
      "text": "Now, with more daring references --"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 398400.0,
      "end_time": 401560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 401800.0,
      "end_time": 402800.0,
      "text": "I can have more fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 403560.0,
      "end_time": 406536.0,
      "text": "But of course, I know that eventually things become so obscure"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 406560.0,
      "end_time": 408456.0,
      "text": "that I start losing some of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 408480.0,
      "end_time": 413960.0,
      "text": "So as a designer, it's absolutely key to have a good understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 413120.0,
      "end_time": 416440.0,
      "text": "of the visual and cultural vocabulary of your audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 418000.0,
      "end_time": 423256.0,
      "text": "With this image here, a comment on the Olympics in Athens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 423280.0,
      "end_time": 425376.0,
      "text": "I assumed that the reader of the \"New Yorker\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 425400.0,
      "end_time": 428335.0,
      "text": "would have some rudimentary idea of Greek art."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 428360.0,
      "end_time": 430200.0,
      "text": "If you don't, the image doesn't work."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 430880.0,
      "end_time": 433616.0,
      "text": "But if you do, you might even appreciate the small detail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 433640.0,
      "end_time": 436496.0,
      "text": "like the beer-can pattern here on the bottom of the vase."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 436520.0,
      "end_time": 438200.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 439600.0,
      "end_time": 443736.0,
      "text": "A recurring discussion I have with magazine editors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 443760.0,
      "end_time": 445736.0,
      "text": "who are usually word people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 445760.0,
      "end_time": 448360.0,
      "text": "is that their audience, you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 449320.0,
      "end_time": 452896.0,
      "text": "are much better at making radical leaps with images"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 452920.0,
      "end_time": 454640.0,
      "text": "than they're being given credit for."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 455240.0,
      "end_time": 459536.0,
      "text": "And the only thing I find frustrating is that they often seem to push me"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 459560.0,
      "end_time": 463136.0,
      "text": "towards a small set of really tired visual clichés"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 463160.0,
      "end_time": 464776.0,
      "text": "that are considered safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 464800.0,
      "end_time": 467776.0,
      "text": "You know, it's the businessman climbing up a ladder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 467800.0,
      "end_time": 470896.0,
      "text": "and then the ladder moves, morphs into a stock market graph,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 470920.0,
      "end_time": 473336.0,
      "text": "and anything with dollar signs; that's always good."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 473360.0,
      "end_time": 474976.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 475000.0,
      "end_time": 478816.0,
      "text": "If there are editorial decision makers here in the audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 478840.0,
      "end_time": 480616.0,
      "text": "I want to give you a piece of advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 480640.0,
      "end_time": 483536.0,
      "text": "Every time a drawing like this is published,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 483560.0,
      "end_time": 485416.0,
      "text": "a baby panda will die."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 485440.0,
      "end_time": 486536.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 486560.0,
      "end_time": 487776.0,
      "text": "Literally."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 487800.0,
      "end_time": 489136.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 489160.0,
      "end_time": 493736.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 493760.0,
      "end_time": 497560.0,
      "text": "When is a visual cliché good or bad?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 497800.0,
      "end_time": 498895.0,
      "text": "It's a fine line."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 498920.0,
      "end_time": 501216.0,
      "text": "And it really depends on the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 501240.0,
      "end_time": 504976.0,
      "text": "In 2011, during the earthquake and the tsunami in Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 505000.0,
      "end_time": 507176.0,
      "text": "I was thinking of a cover."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 507200.0,
      "end_time": 509656.0,
      "text": "And I went through the classic symbols:"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 509680.0,
      "end_time": 510976.0,
      "text": "the Japanese flag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 511000.0,
      "end_time": 514360.0,
      "text": "\"The Great Wave\" by Hokusai, one of the greatest drawings ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 515520.0,
      "end_time": 518135.0,
      "text": "And then the story changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 518159.0,
      "end_time": 521319.0,
      "text": "when the situation at the power plant in Fukushima got out of hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 522200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526816.0,
      "text": "And I remember these TV images of the workers in hazmat suits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 526840.0,
      "end_time": 528296.0,
      "text": "just walking through the site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 528320.0,
      "end_time": 531976.0,
      "text": "and what struck me was how quiet and serene it was."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 532000.0,
      "end_time": 535400.0,
      "text": "And so I wanted to create an image of a silent catastrophe."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 536200.0,
      "end_time": 537920.0,
      "text": "And that's the image I came up with."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 539120.0,
      "end_time": 540736.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 540760.0,
      "end_time": 541976.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 542000.0,
      "end_time": 544640.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 545280.0,
      "end_time": 549600.0,
      "text": "What I want to do is create an aha moment, for you, for the reader."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 550200.0,
      "end_time": 552160.0,
      "text": "And unfortunately, that does not mean"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 552400.0,
      "end_time": 554560.0,
      "text": "that I have an aha moment when I create these images."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 555520.0,
      "end_time": 556776.0,
      "text": "I never sit at my desk"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 556800.0,
      "end_time": 559760.0,
      "text": "with the proverbial light bulb going off in my head."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 561200.0,
      "end_time": 564160.0,
      "text": "What it takes is actually a very slow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 564400.0,
      "end_time": 567456.0,
      "text": "unsexy process of minimal design decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 567480.0,
      "end_time": 569800.0,
      "text": "that then, when I'm lucky, lead to a good idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 571960.0,
      "end_time": 574616.0,
      "text": "So one day, I'm on a train, and I'm trying to decode"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 574640.0,
      "end_time": 576840.0,
      "text": "the graphic rules for drops on a window."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 577520.0,
      "end_time": 578776.0,
      "text": "And eventually I realize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 578800.0,
      "end_time": 582295.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, it's the background blurry upside-down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 582320.0,
      "end_time": 583696.0,
      "text": "contained in a sharp image.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 583720.0,
      "end_time": 585596.0,
      "text": "And I thought, wow, that's really cool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 585610.0,
      "end_time": 587986.0,
      "text": "and I have absolutely no idea what to do with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 588160.0,
      "end_time": 590175.0,
      "text": "A while later, I'm back in New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 590200.0,
      "end_time": 594560.0,
      "text": "and I draw this image of being stuck on the Brooklyn bridge in a traffic jam."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 595240.0,
      "end_time": 597600.0,
      "text": "It's really annoying, but also kind of poetic."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 598960.0,
      "end_time": 600216.0,
      "text": "And only later I realized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 600240.0,
      "end_time": 603520.0,
      "text": "I can take both of these ideas and put them together in this idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 604760.0,
      "end_time": 607880.0,
      "text": "And what I want to do is not show a realistic scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 609160.0,
      "end_time": 611736.0,
      "text": "But, maybe like poetry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 611760.0,
      "end_time": 615216.0,
      "text": "make you aware that you already had this image with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 615240.0,
      "end_time": 617960.0,
      "text": "but only now I've unearthed it"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 617120.0,
      "end_time": 620720.0,
      "text": "and made you realize that you were carrying it with you all along."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 621760.0,
      "end_time": 625960.0,
      "text": "But like poetry, this is a very delicate process"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 625120.0,
      "end_time": 629480.0,
      "text": "that is neither efficient nor scalable, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 630720.0,
      "end_time": 634256.0,
      "text": "And maybe the most important skill for an artist"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 634280.0,
      "end_time": 635480.0,
      "text": "is really empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 636640.0,
      "end_time": 639696.0,
      "text": "You need craft and you need --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 639720.0,
      "end_time": 641256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 641280.0,
      "end_time": 642536.0,
      "text": "you need creativity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 642560.0,
      "end_time": 644950.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 644120.0,
      "end_time": 645336.0,
      "text": "thank you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 645360.0,
      "end_time": 647496.0,
      "text": "to come up with an image like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 647520.0,
      "end_time": 649776.0,
      "text": "But then you need to step back"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 649800.0,
      "end_time": 652920.0,
      "text": "and look at what you've done from the perspective of the reader."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 653920.0,
      "end_time": 658560.0,
      "text": "I've tried to become a better artist by becoming a better observer of images."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 659280.0,
      "end_time": 661616.0,
      "text": "And for that, I started an exercise for myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 661640.0,
      "end_time": 663856.0,
      "text": "which I call Sunday sketching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 663880.0,
      "end_time": 668976.0,
      "text": "which meant, on a Sunday, I would take a random object I found around the house"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 669000.0,
      "end_time": 673416.0,
      "text": "and try to see if that object could trigger an idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 673440.0,
      "end_time": 676360.0,
      "text": "that had nothing to do with the original purpose of that item."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 677160.0,
      "end_time": 680160.0,
      "text": "And it usually just means I'm blank for a long while."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 681160.0,
      "end_time": 684695.0,
      "text": "And the only trick that eventually works is if I open my mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 684720.0,
      "end_time": 688560.0,
      "text": "and run through every image I have stored up there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 688800.0,
      "end_time": 689640.0,
      "text": "and see if something clicks."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 690640.0,
      "end_time": 695160.0,
      "text": "And if it does, just add a few lines of ink to connect --"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 695400.0,
      "end_time": 697959.0,
      "text": "to preserve this very short moment of inspiration."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 700200.0,
      "end_time": 702496.0,
      "text": "And the great lesson there"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 702520.0,
      "end_time": 705736.0,
      "text": "was that the real magic doesn't happen on paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 705760.0,
      "end_time": 707560.0,
      "text": "It happens in the mind of the viewer."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 708320.0,
      "end_time": 713960.0,
      "text": "When your expectations and your knowledge clash with my artistic intentions."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 715960.0,
      "end_time": 718856.0,
      "text": "Your interaction with an image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 718880.0,
      "end_time": 723176.0,
      "text": "your ability to read, question, be bothered or bored or inspired"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 723200.0,
      "end_time": 724416.0,
      "text": "by an image"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 724440.0,
      "end_time": 726880.0,
      "text": "is as important as my artistic contribution."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 727960.0,
      "end_time": 732200.0,
      "text": "Because that's what turns an artistic statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 733720.0,
      "end_time": 735320.0,
      "text": "really, into a creative dialogue."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 737400.0,
      "end_time": 739496.0,
      "text": "And so, your skill at reading images"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 739520.0,
      "end_time": 740760.0,
      "text": "is not only amazing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 741560.0,
      "end_time": 743400.0,
      "text": "it is what makes my art possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 744880.0,
      "end_time": 747336.0,
      "text": "And for that, I thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 747360.0,
      "end_time": 750456.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 750480.0,
      "end_time": 755800.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 756000.0,
      "end_time": 757216.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 757240.0,
      "end_time": 761800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}